00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:14,890
 1993

221
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:19,970
 What? This is...

222
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:23,920
 You'll just serve ten years in jail, no more.

223
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,860
 The new administration has taken office.

224
00:16:25,860 --> 00:16:29,840
 It's time to round up some chaebol ( conglomerate owner )  to show the public how "righteous" we are.

225
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:33,930
 So I'm your target? And you're here to arrest me?

226
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:37,410
 We'd be having this conversation in my office if that were the case.

227
00:16:37,410 --> 00:16:41,140
 Why do you think I suggested this lunch meeting?

228
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:45,230
 I'd like to run for office during the upcoming general election.

229
00:16:46,860 --> 00:16:49,230
 Join hands with me,

230
00:16:49,230 --> 00:16:53,320
 and I'll bury this for you.

231
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:58,260
 I'm sure we can do a lot together.

232
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,460
 Thank you, sir.

233
00:17:17,320 --> 00:17:21,150
I was wrong. It was nothing but an ill-fated decision.

234
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:25,910
You must know that I don't have many days left to live.

235
00:17:26,950 --> 00:17:31,490
We could go to jail together, hand in hand.

236
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:40,600
You see, we've known each other for a long time.

237
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:46,390
It'd be nice to reminisce about the good old days together in jail.

238
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:50,920
This is my last request and threat.

239
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:56,390
Put Seong Jun back where he belongs.

240
00:17:56,390 --> 00:18:00,560
And do not contact my children again.

241
00:18:02,490 --> 00:18:04,960
I'm sure you get the message.

242
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:32,030
Let's take care of him. I'll get ready, sir.

243
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:36,440
- It's too risky.
 - When was it not?

244
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:39,210
We're dealing with Chairman Kim here.

245
00:18:58,210 --> 00:19:00,560
Kim Geon Yeong.

246
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:17,060
 Help!

247
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:23,670
 Oppa. Oppa! Oppa!

248
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:30,490
 Help! Oppa. Oppa. Oppa.

249
00:19:30,490 --> 00:19:32,290
Oppa.

250
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:43,860
Do you really think a mere prosecutor can take me down?

251
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:54,020
Unfortunately, this is my job. I'm just following orders. So no hard feelings, please.

252
00:19:56,570 --> 00:20:00,300
Looks like this will take a while. Do you want some ox bone soup?

253
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:04,970
Oh, wait. Do rich heirs not eat stuff like that?

254
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:15,620
We're letting Mr. Kim Seong Jun go.

255
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:33,080
Mr. Kim Seong Jun has been released.

