01:01:34,840 --> 01:01:41,160
If the work this time gets buried for power, it'll be hard for everyone to be safe.

757
01:01:41,160 --> 01:01:43,290
Me, you too,

758
01:01:43,290 --> 01:01:45,280
Seong Ho too.

759
01:01:48,330 --> 01:01:50,520
Don't worry, you kids!

760
01:01:50,520 --> 01:01:54,110
If we fail, I'll go down for everything.

761
01:01:54,110 --> 01:01:56,730
There won't be any such thing.

762
01:01:56,730 --> 01:01:59,900
What do you mean? That's what Nongae would've said.

763
01:01:59,900 --> 01:02:00,830
What's this about?

764
01:02:00,830 --> 01:02:06,010
Right? We're in the same boat, so we'll share fate.

765
01:02:06,010 --> 01:02:08,730
Is there some serious matter?

766
01:02:08,730 --> 01:02:10,310
No, there isn't.

767
01:02:10,310 --> 01:02:13,790
Our work is always serious, no? Don't pay any attention.

768
01:02:13,790 --> 01:02:15,570
Hui Wu's mom has a lot of worries

769
01:02:15,570 --> 01:02:19,300
that since all you guys meet are bad people, you may get harassed.

770
01:02:19,300 --> 01:02:21,720
Father, please do not worry.

771
01:02:21,720 --> 01:02:23,170
I will protect them well.

772
01:02:23,170 --> 01:02:27,380
Just hearing you say so feels reassuring. Dear, do you not have something to say at this moment?

773
01:02:27,380 --> 01:02:29,440
Director, do you have anything you'd like to eat?

774
01:02:29,440 --> 01:02:32,220
Why wouldn't there be? Let's bring the kitchen in its entirety.

775
01:02:32,220 --> 01:02:34,790
Let's braise everything and bring them to him.

776
01:02:37,120 --> 01:02:38,940
Who will protect whom?

777
01:02:38,940 --> 01:02:44,050
Have you not seen Hui Wu flying about? We'll be fortunate if we don't become a burden.

778
01:02:44,050 --> 01:02:45,760
What do you mean a burden?

779
01:02:45,760 --> 01:02:50,080
We each protect each other.

780
01:02:51,060 --> 01:02:53,860
Here, let's have a drink.

781
01:03:13,100 --> 01:03:15,400
What is the matter?

782
01:03:16,250 --> 01:03:18,140
 I would like to see the Assemblyman.

783
01:03:18,140 --> 01:03:21,200
The Assemblyman doesn't receive visits other than scheduled appointments.

784
01:03:21,200 --> 01:03:24,950
Please convey that it's urgent business concerning Chief Prosecutor Kim Seok Hun.

785
01:03:24,950 --> 01:03:27,220
Then, after you've made an appointment, please return.

786
01:03:27,220 --> 01:03:30,990
 Manager Ha, I'm not someone who comes on pointless matters.

787
01:03:30,990 --> 01:03:34,560
That decision is, of course, the Assemblyman's part.

788
01:03:35,900 --> 01:03:39,060
Then, I will ask him.

789
01:03:47,240 --> 01:03:49,460
 Please come in.

790
01:04:15,400 --> 01:04:16,900
Finally, I've arrived.

791
01:04:16,900 --> 01:04:22,150
 The heart of power in Korea. And the gathering place of trash.

792
01:04:48,560 --> 01:04:52,770
Assemblyman, Prosecutor Kim Hui Wu has arrived.

793
01:04:52,770 --> 01:04:54,790
Let him enter.

794
01:05:20,870 --> 01:05:23,240
Have you been well?

795
01:05:24,550 --> 01:05:26,930
So what is the matter?

796
01:05:28,030 --> 01:05:32,580
I will catch the Chief Prosecutor Kim Seok Hun.

797
01:05:33,960 --> 01:05:40,990

798
01:05:42,390 --> 01:05:46,510
♫  Dear, All your things you've done  ♫

799
01:05:46,510 --> 01:05:49,740
♫  We are here to wreck it up  ♫

800
01:05:49,740 --> 01:05:55,940
♫  Who knows, how will it go?  ♫

801
01:05:59,220 --> 01:06:03,540
♫  Hiding in black and white  ♫

802
01:06:03,540 --> 01:06:06,630
♫  We are here to find the truth  ♫

803
01:06:06,630 --> 01:06:08,050
♫  Give up, I warn you so  ♫

804
01:06:08,050 --> 01:06:11,340
 Again My Life

805
01:06:11,340 --> 01:06:15,550
 The trigger has already been pulled.

806
01:06:15,550 --> 01:06:17,200
 Let's make a deal.

807
01:06:17,200 --> 01:06:21,360
 It's time for those who were waiting in silence to shine.

808
01:06:21,360 --> 01:06:24,850
 That bastard, Kim Hui Wu, doesn't he seem dangerous?

809
01:06:24,850 --> 01:06:26,980
 Even if I can know the truth—

810
01:06:26,980 --> 01:06:28,750
 You have no right to stop me.

811
01:06:28,750 --> 01:06:34,750
 Should I go along with him, or if not...

812
01:06:34,750 --> 01:06:38,660
 I will shut the mouth of the righteous lawyer.

813
01:06:38,660 --> 01:06:40,530
♫  what they say  ♫

814
01:06:40,530 --> 01:06:44,340
♫  At the end, They'll know  ♫

